<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8"
    pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/OwlCarousel2/2.3.4/assets/owl.carousel.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/OwlCarousel2/2.3.4/assets/owl.theme.default.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/Testimonials.css" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"/>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section class="testimony-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row no-gutters justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-md-12 py-5 pl-md-5">
            <div class="py-md-5">
              <div class="heading-section mb-4 text-center">
                <span class="subheading">What our customers are saying</span>
                <h2 class="mb-5">Customer Reviews</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-testimony owl-carousel">
                <div class="item">
                  <div class="testimony-wrap pb-4">
                    <div class="text">
                      <p class="mb-4">
                        Wonderful experience. Beautiful hotel with great
                        service. The food and drinks at the restaurant and bar
                        were excellent and reasonably priced. I hope to stay
                        here again. Thanks for your hospitality.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex">
                      <div
                        class="user-img"
                        style="background-image: url(/images/Testimonials/Curtis.jpg)"
                      ></div>
                      <div class="pos ml-3">
                        <p class="name">Ann Curtis</p>
                        <span class="position">Traveller</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                  <div class="testimony-wrap pb-4">
                    <div class="text">
                      <p class="mb-4">
                        Paraiso Hotel is amazing! In Siargao, where you choose to stay
                        can really make or break your trip. Since you can only
                        swim in the ocean at high tide, a pool is an absolute
                        must. 
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex">
                      <div
                        class="user-img"
                        style="background-image: url(/images/Testimonials/Coco.jpg)"
                      ></div>
                      <div class="pos ml-3">
                        <p class="name">Coco Martin</p>
                        <span class="position">Traveller</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                  <div class="testimony-wrap pb-4">
                    <div class="text">
                      <p class="mb-4">
                        Excellent experience, I love the resort so much.
                        Bathroom has a unique style. I love the food so much and
                        the staffs are very accommodating and friendly, highly
                        recommend hotel.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex">
                      <div
                        class="user-img"
                        style="background-image: url(/images/Testimonials/Marian.jpg)"
                      ></div>
                      <div class="pos ml-3">
                        <p class="name">Marian Rivera</p>
                        <span class="position">Traveller</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                  <div class="testimony-wrap pb-4">
                    <div class="text">
                      <p class="mb-4">
                        The hotel is by far the best place to stay on the
                        island. We stayed here for three nights. Had a lovely
                        time. You've got the beach, a pool, a spa, the whole
                        package.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex">
                      <div
                        class="user-img"
                        style="background-image: url(/images/Testimonials/Richard.jpg)"
                      ></div>
                      <div class="pos ml-3">
                        <p class="name">Alden Richards</p>
                        <span class="position">Traveller</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="item">
                  <div class="testimony-wrap pb-4">
                    <div class="text">
                      <p class="mb-4">
                        We had an amazing time during our stay.The room we
                        stayed in was so tidy and the room was so spacious.
                        Their beachfront is a peaceful haven with its individual
                        lounges like out of a travel magazine.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex">
                      <div
                        class="user-img"
                        style="background-image: url(/images/Testimonials/Liza.jpg)"
                      ></div>
                      <div class="pos ml-3">
                        <p class="name">Liza Soberano</p>
                        <span class="position">Traveller</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="item">
                  <div class="testimony-wrap pb-4">
                    <div class="text">
                      <p class="mb-4">
                        Most definitely would recommend this place to anyone
                        wanting to travel to Siargao. Great service, amenities,
                        views and villa. I would rebook when travelling back
                        here in a heartbeat!
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex">
                      <div
                        class="user-img"
                        style="background-image: url(/images/Testimonials/Piolo.jpg)"
                      ></div>
                      <div class="pos ml-3">
                        <p class="name">Piolo Pascual</p>
                        <span class="position">Traveller</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/OwlCarousel2/2.3.4/owl.carousel.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/Testimonials.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
